Most critical skills/experiences:
- Strong ownership: you can take ambiguous problems, define the plan, and execute with minimal supervision.
- Stakeholder management and crisp communication (written + verbal), including tradeoffs and decision docs.
- Solid analytical/technical judgment relevant to the role—enough depth to evaluate options, spot risks early, and ensure quality.
